    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Men and women

          -  minimum 40 years

          -  Chronic Kidney disease

          -  Estimated GFR (eGFR) between 30 and 90 ml/min

          -  Diabetes Mellitus type II

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Nephrotic Syndrome

          -  Anamnestic or clinical signs of significant heart, lung, lever, kidney and brain
